<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="500">3.2. Margins</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Carry out the settings for the page margins of the documents in this area. The margins are important for automatic page breaks and the positioning of mandatory elements in the document. Pay attention to the information provided in <a href="#table-documents-margins">Table 2</a>.</p>
