<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Value of items (net)</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Net value of the items (excluding VAT)
In addition, select whether the value of items is displayed summed up for all VAT rates, summed up per VAT rate or per VAT rate if B2B. <br>
